                                  K                (K, V)                 K, List(V)          (K, V)            (K, V)                  V - count
    ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
   |                                           .  Dear, 1         .                                                       |
   |                       . Deer Bear River . .  Bear, 1         .                                                       |
   |                    .                      .  River, 1        .       Bear(1,1)   ...     Bear, 2                     |
